{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A vampire-slaying pachinko roguelike deckbuilder. Collect a powerful deck of cards, strategize, aim, and pop pegs to power up and deal massive damage with relic synergies. Play as one of the unlikely heroes, conquer Transylvania, and free the people in this turn-based RPG.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_mobius-strip_froggy-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dynamic Deck Building </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create a unique deck by choosing cards wisely. Discover hundreds of cards to defeat wicked creatures and regain power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_cards-4.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pachinko-style Gameplay </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategically hit pegs to power up your cards. Uncover game-changing relics throughout the world to enhance your deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_spiral-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ever-Changing Transylvania </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maps change with each journey. Choose paths, face different enemies, encounter random events, and confront various bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_map-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paris Transylvania features a nostalgic cartoony art style mixed with retro elements, blending Peggle, Peglin and Slay The Spire mechanics with a fresh twist in both format and gameplay. Play cards in any order and choose your path without RNG. The boss fights will keep you on your toes, with extravagant creeps and heart-pounding retro minigames adding to the excitement.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736422232","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/page.bg.jpg?t=1736422232","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736422232","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736422232","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2470480,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A vampire-slaying pachinko roguelike deckbuilder. Collect a powerful deck of cards, strategize, aim, and pop pegs to power up and deal massive damage with relic synergies. Play as one of the unlikely heroes, conquer Transylvania, and free the people in this turn-based RPG.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_mobius-strip_froggy-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dynamic Deck Building </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create a unique deck by choosing cards wisely. Discover hundreds of cards to defeat wicked creatures and regain power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_cards-4.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pachinko-style Gameplay </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategically hit pegs to power up your cards. Uncover game-changing relics throughout the world to enhance your deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_spiral-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ever-Changing Transylvania </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maps change with each journey. Choose paths, face different enemies, encounter random events, and confront various bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/extras/paris-transylvania_map-2.gif?t=1736422232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paris Transylvania features a nostalgic cartoony art style mixed with retro elements, blending Peggle, Peglin and Slay The Spire mechanics with a fresh twist in both format and gameplay. Play cards in any order and choose your path without RNG. The boss fights will keep you on your toes, with extravagant creeps and heart-pounding retro minigames adding to the excitement.</p>","developers":["Magneticlake"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459560/header.jpg?t=1736422232","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"All intellectual property rights, including copyrights and trademarks, associated with this product or intellectual property, are owned by Magneticlake.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 14.04 LTS<br></